#BoycottBigTech2021
Join us in boycotting everyone and anyone who opposes freedom of speech. March 1st through May 1st - Take a stand! We The People Dictate the laws in this country, not big business. Our founding fathers would be sick to the core if they were alive today! 

Boycott list -
ABC, NBC, CBS, Bloomberg News, CNN, Fox News, Amazon, Bed Bath and Beyond, Kohl’s, Twitter, Snapchat, Vimeo, Instagram, Facebook. 

Spread the word, print flyers, use the hashtag, and sign the petition showing your dedication to the cause - https://signup.com/m/#/organizer/login

Free Speech Alternatives -
OANN, GAB.com, GABtv, NTD, Epoch Times, Parler (Once back up) Telegram, CloutHub
